name: lake oconee luxury homes
details: {{"Presenting the Ultimate Luxury Lake Estate, Your Own Private Lake Resort at Reynolds Lake Oconee, minutes from the amenities and the Ritz by car or by boat. Crafted with unparalleled attention to details by premier builders Jones and Jones, no expense was spared in creating this masterpiece that boasts superior craftsmanship and luxury amenities. Situated on an acre of prime lakefront property, soak in big lake views and the picturesque Jack Nicklaus golf course vistas every day. Enjoy sunset views and watch July 4th fireworks from your pool deck or private boat dock, adding a touch of magic to your evenings.With over 7,700 square feet of pure quality and luxury, this home uniquely features five oversized garages, catering to the most discerning of car enthusiasts and a separate pool house.Step inside to be captivated by a grand great room adorned with abundant natural light and majestic lake views, seamlessly blending indoor and outdoor living. Entertain in the high-end kitchen equipped with Wolf and Subzero appliances and a wine bar while the dining room opens to an expansive screened porch with a fireplace,perfect for al fresco dining, and a balcony overlooking the lake. The keeping room, an extension of the living and dining area, is complemented by glass doors that connects the porches and the outdoor deck overlooking the luxurious pool area."}
